{"tid":1631972,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"正式宣佈今晚風向係同勇武割蓆","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:48:15.000Z","uid":20640,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"25935fe9b61cadb6ce6347af948c26ff534bb788","tid":1631972,"uid":20640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:32.000Z","msg":"十一國殤全日上唔到連登<br />\n點解今日全日冇事嘅? 響張床發夢中間擲醒碌下連登<br />\n屌你老味全撚部po都係講前線癲咗<br />\n搞到和理非手足唔知點配合 引大家內閧重合割蓆嘅話題上<br />\n屌你老母 同林奠個賊婆講嘅野咁撚似嘅<br />\n諗兩諗原來今日連登全日冇事就係要配合條死柒婆帶出割蓆風向<br />\n建議手足們今晚離遠連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2126ec92c97baf950b6c38f2d3b23fdc7e1359","tid":1631972,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:44:06.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"2b6d5a91acbfdd9a62b02afbc3997a0d9ed607fa","tid":1631972,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:45:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0a6ac79d13e97385df8e387ee69d948c4df7017","tid":1631972,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:45:45.000Z","msg":"yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd425b46df820da65874bb0b75a2823d3b7c121c","tid":1631972,"uid":48315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:16.000Z","msg":"好撚明顯<br />\n又話勇武失控<br />\n又話勇武搞到人權法過唔到<br />\n又叫勇武休息<br />\n屌你老母 真係當勇武白痴架"},{"pid":"8e906b52461d0e7cea42c7990830d4e0e1afb83f","tid":1631972,"uid":179378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14fb84a46d947381fb6f80131cd310c8b3f75e4","tid":1631972,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e9718ab712954b7cbff08555d1d75815454c71b","tid":1631972,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:58.000Z","msg":"不如連登熄燈啦"},{"pid":"fe271a12a1b2e808391538bc1a6de28bc7411e85","tid":1631972,"uid":5889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:47:02.000Z","msg":"直接block 唔洗理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d361eb8ce98078117c144859989912400e9cb913","tid":1631972,"uid":259675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:47:21.000Z","msg":"前線不嬲發夢唔上連登 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成班連登仔自己鬧自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e324b8c4d4e1fe